highlights.text: “Jhol” by Maanu and Annural Khalid has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 130 days straight.
“Solcito” by Miguel Bueno and Juan Duque is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #2.
ATLXS has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” is the highest at #5.
“Se Essa Bunda For Uma Empresa” by Chefin and LB Único is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 11 spots at #87.
